snippet.title: Manalith - Gameplay 2
snippet.description:
Don't forget to wishlist Manalith on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1408810/Manalith/

Here's a new gameplay video from Manalith. A lot has changed since the previous video, but most important is that many of the Manaliths now cause parts of the world to change once they are activated.

Manaliths might open up access to treasures, create short cuts between parts of the world, or activate lights that can help guide you from place to place.
